1
00:00:21,070 --> 00:00:24,180
♪The breeze of the 1990s drifts by♪

2
00:00:24,350 --> 00:00:27,180
♪Memories slowly flicker past♪

3
00:00:27,650 --> 00:00:31,430
♪My heartbeat
rises and falls with the tune♪

4
00:00:31,500 --> 00:00:34,580
♪The story quietly begins here♪

5
00:00:35,330 --> 00:00:38,640
♪Under the dim lights, our eyes meet♪

6
00:00:38,710 --> 00:00:41,850
♪Time seems to stand still♪

7
00:00:42,350 --> 00:00:45,990
♪Your smile
breaks through the clouds like sun♪

8
00:00:46,060 --> 00:00:49,150
♪Melting the snow deep in my heart♪

9
00:00:49,580 --> 00:00:53,090
♪Street posters spread signals of love♪

10
00:00:53,150 --> 00:00:56,110
♪Our story slowly begins to ferment♪

11
00:00:56,800 --> 00:01:00,730
♪Hand in hand,
going through every dusk corner♪

12
00:01:00,930 --> 00:01:04,800
♪The taste of happiness is so subtle♪

13
00:01:05,480 --> 00:01:08,740
♪Crossing back to the 1990s stage♪

14
00:01:09,150 --> 00:01:12,480
♪You're my most beautiful surprise♪

15
00:01:12,790 --> 00:01:16,210
♪Love's flame burns within my heart♪

16
00:01:16,680 --> 00:01:19,710
♪Not afraid of obstacles ahead♪

17
00:01:20,180 --> 00:01:23,560
♪Sway with the rhythm.
Feel your heart pound♪

18
00:01:23,660 --> 00:01:27,150
♪This love will never change♪

19
00:01:27,950 --> 00:01:35,080
♪We hold tight in this crazy era♪

20
00:01:35,160 --> 00:01:40,060
♪1990s love is what we rely on♪

21
00:01:40,100 --> 00:01:42,070
=Once More Love in 1995=

22
00:01:42,260 --> 00:01:44,912
=Episode 16=

23
00:01:45,912 --> 00:01:47,391
Am I a loser?

24
00:01:48,119 --> 00:01:49,679
Even my own sister hates my guts.

25
00:01:50,919 --> 00:01:52,279
Yeah, you are.

26
00:01:53,962 --> 00:01:55,603
You try to make everyone happy

27
00:01:55,603 --> 00:01:56,643
and everything perfect,

28
00:01:56,643 --> 00:01:57,962
but that often backfires.

29
00:02:00,960 --> 00:02:01,925
Did you come to mock me?

30
00:02:01,925 --> 00:02:03,445
Don't think of me as that awful.

31
00:02:04,660 --> 00:02:05,850
I came to praise you instead.

32
00:02:09,399 --> 00:02:11,320
Thanks to your wise and

33
00:02:11,320 --> 00:02:12,200
decisive handling,

34
00:02:12,480 --> 00:02:15,119
you exposed that the expired food
was Ji Hong's doing

35
00:02:15,399 --> 00:02:17,399
and immediately published
a public apology.

36
00:02:18,119 --> 00:02:19,800
After the gutter oil incident,

37
00:02:19,800 --> 00:02:22,159
you arranged for customers to tour
the factory right away

38
00:02:22,599 --> 00:02:24,275
and proved that Jinxin Food is safe.

39
00:02:24,625 --> 00:02:25,984
That whole series of moves

40
00:02:25,984 --> 00:02:27,512
was smooth

41
00:02:27,512 --> 00:02:28,832
and flawless.

42
00:02:29,562 --> 00:02:32,080
Qin Mo, you've done a great job,

43
00:02:33,800 --> 00:02:34,999
but you're not a superhero.

44
00:02:35,279 --> 00:02:36,760
Don't push yourself so hard.

45
00:02:39,360 --> 00:02:40,320
You're not bad either.

46
00:02:40,920 --> 00:02:43,999
I learned the public sentiment trick
from you.

47
00:02:44,537 --> 00:02:47,097
Mr. Qin, how come you still look unhappy

48
00:02:47,097 --> 00:02:48,977
after all that praise?

49
00:02:56,559 --> 00:02:58,080
Shanshan, why are you out of bed?

50
00:02:58,760 --> 00:03:00,775
Yan, I can dance again.

51
00:03:04,999 --> 00:03:06,960
You're panting now.

52
00:03:06,999 --> 00:03:07,960
Sit down and rest.

53
00:03:07,960 --> 00:03:08,879
I'm not tired.

54
00:03:09,159 --> 00:03:11,279
Just thinking about
getting back on stage

55
00:03:11,279 --> 00:03:12,119
makes me thrilled.

56
00:03:15,360 --> 00:03:18,119
(Mom, since you want to
return to the stage)

57
00:03:18,119 --> 00:03:19,399
(and pursue your dream,)

58
00:03:19,999 --> 00:03:22,399
(I'll support you in applying
to Juilliard.)

59
00:03:26,719 --> 00:03:28,279
You're still up, Qin?

60
00:03:30,599 --> 00:03:31,920
How's your leg?

61
00:03:32,200 --> 00:03:33,119
Much better.

62
00:03:38,320 --> 00:03:39,159
Qin,

63
00:03:40,360 --> 00:03:42,275
I want to apply to Juilliard.

64
00:03:44,119 --> 00:03:44,700
Qin,

65
00:03:44,812 --> 00:03:46,132
this is not an impulsive decision.

66
00:03:46,760 --> 00:03:47,599
All these years,

67
00:03:47,599 --> 00:03:49,200
you protected me so well.

68
00:03:49,520 --> 00:03:51,580
I never saw how dangerous
people's hearts could be.

69
00:03:52,200 --> 00:03:54,839
A few sweet words were enough
to fool me,

70
00:03:55,119 --> 00:03:56,760
and I almost ruined my life.

71
00:03:58,200 --> 00:04:00,240
Also, I've caused you and Yan
so much trouble.

72
00:04:00,599 --> 00:04:01,599
But don't worry.

73
00:04:01,719 --> 00:04:04,080
I can take responsibility
for myself now.

74
00:04:04,760 --> 00:04:08,159
Whether my future
is beautiful or full of storms,

75
00:04:08,599 --> 00:04:10,240
I want to experience it myself.

76
00:04:12,399 --> 00:04:14,480
Besides, now that Jiamin's back,

77
00:04:14,520 --> 00:04:17,520
I don't want her to feel bad
because you take my side.

78
00:04:18,200 --> 00:04:20,159
She still cares a lot about you.

79
00:04:21,680 --> 00:04:22,200
Alright.

80
00:04:22,660 --> 00:04:23,599
I respect your decision.

81
00:04:24,560 --> 00:04:26,320
But remember,
don't push yourself too hard.

82
00:04:26,719 --> 00:04:28,479
If anything happens, come home anytime.

83
00:04:28,660 --> 00:04:29,990
I'll always be your big brother.

84
00:04:30,159 --> 00:04:30,960
Okay.

85
00:04:31,760 --> 00:04:33,719
Qin, I'll go to bed then.

86
00:04:34,359 --> 00:04:34,839
Mm.

87
00:04:37,399 --> 00:04:38,320
About Zhuang Yan,

88
00:04:38,680 --> 00:04:40,466
there's something
I've wanted to tell you.

89
00:04:43,560 --> 00:04:44,399
Actually, she...

90
00:04:44,399 --> 00:04:46,000
She's not really Yan.

91
00:04:49,000 --> 00:04:51,187
You knew it all along?

92
00:04:52,399 --> 00:04:54,960
No matter how distant,
she's still a cousin.

93
00:04:55,050 --> 00:04:57,050
I could tell that with a test.

94
00:04:58,080 --> 00:04:59,599
Why didn't you expose her?

95
00:05:01,279 --> 00:05:02,080
Well,

96
00:05:02,399 --> 00:05:04,680
since the day she started
pretending to be Yan,

97
00:05:04,680 --> 00:05:06,200
she's looked out for me in every way.

98
00:05:06,760 --> 00:05:09,200
From Zhou Zeyang to Jinxin,

99
00:05:09,599 --> 00:05:12,279
she's always been protecting me.

100
00:05:14,120 --> 00:05:16,919
But she's not related to you,
and her background is unclear.

101
00:05:17,279 --> 00:05:19,159
Aren't you afraid
she might bring you danger?

102
00:05:19,560 --> 00:05:21,760
To most Jinxin employees,

103
00:05:21,760 --> 00:05:23,599
I'm not related to you either.

104
00:05:23,599 --> 00:05:25,359
But you're still good to me.

105
00:05:25,760 --> 00:05:28,479
Aren't you afraid
I might bring you danger?

106
00:05:30,120 --> 00:05:32,200
Yan always looks out for me.

107
00:05:32,599 --> 00:05:33,960
Without her,

108
00:05:34,159 --> 00:05:36,320
I'd still be fooled by Zhou Zeyang.

109
00:05:37,080 --> 00:05:37,919
Qin,

110
00:05:38,279 --> 00:05:40,919
I hope you won't do anything to her
just because of her identity.

111
00:05:44,399 --> 00:05:45,200
Alright.

112
00:05:46,399 --> 00:05:47,200
That's good.

113
00:05:47,599 --> 00:05:48,640
Go get some rest.

114
00:06:07,320 --> 00:06:09,380
Ms. Qin, Mr. Qin said
you're not allowed to go out.

115
00:06:09,399 --> 00:06:10,960
I'm going out anyway.

116
00:06:10,960 --> 00:06:12,000
Please, Ms. Qin.

117
00:06:12,000 --> 00:06:13,200
You really can't.

118
00:06:19,799 --> 00:06:21,479
Jiamin!

119
00:06:21,680 --> 00:06:22,359
Jiamin!

120
00:06:25,200 --> 00:06:25,960
Jiamin!

121
00:06:27,320 --> 00:06:28,479
Come on in.

122
00:06:29,200 --> 00:06:29,960
Zeyang!

123
00:06:30,919 --> 00:06:33,200
I knew you'd come for me.

124
00:06:34,120 --> 00:06:36,440
Zeyang, take me away.

125
00:06:37,159 --> 00:06:38,919
I've been worried sick about you.

126
00:06:39,225 --> 00:06:40,865
I'm so glad you're okay.

127
00:06:41,960 --> 00:06:42,760
But

128
00:06:44,760 --> 00:06:46,560
I can't take you away yet.

129
00:06:47,437 --> 00:06:48,300
Why not?

130
00:06:50,320 --> 00:06:51,960
You need to apologize to Qin Mo,

131
00:06:52,080 --> 00:06:53,479
make peace with the Zhuang sisters,

132
00:06:53,799 --> 00:06:55,012
and return to work at Jinxin.

133
00:07:00,612 --> 00:07:02,013
Did I hear you wrong?

134
00:07:03,500 --> 00:07:04,500
Baby,

135
00:07:05,120 --> 00:07:06,080
this is the only way

136
00:07:06,080 --> 00:07:07,399
to lower their guard

137
00:07:07,399 --> 00:07:09,080
and let you go back to Jinxin.

138
00:07:09,500 --> 00:07:11,620
Why do I have go back there?

139
00:07:11,680 --> 00:07:13,200
For our future.

140
00:07:14,462 --> 00:07:16,320
Only if you return to Jinxin

141
00:07:17,120 --> 00:07:19,960
can we work together
to get rid of Zhuang Yan.

142
00:07:20,275 --> 00:07:22,239
As long as Qin Mo sees her true colors,

143
00:07:22,960 --> 00:07:25,680
the grievances between us
will naturally disappear.

144
00:07:27,599 --> 00:07:28,399
Jiamin,

145
00:07:29,680 --> 00:07:30,960
are you willing to

146
00:07:33,000 --> 00:07:34,960
swallow your pride for me?

147
00:07:40,359 --> 00:07:41,960
Why aren't you eating?

148
00:07:42,799 --> 00:07:44,799
Qin Jiamin, just say what you want to say.

149
00:07:45,825 --> 00:07:47,120
I'm afraid you poisoned the food.

150
00:07:51,125 --> 00:07:52,925
I've thought it over
these past few days.

151
00:07:53,212 --> 00:07:54,892
I've decided to break up
with Zhou Zeyang.

152
00:07:57,680 --> 00:07:59,080
What kind of act is this?

153
00:07:59,450 --> 00:08:01,289
You're willing to break up with him?

154
00:08:01,520 --> 00:08:04,250
Who was it that cried, threatened
suicide, and went on hunger strike?

155
00:08:04,719 --> 00:08:07,880
That's when I finally realized

156
00:08:08,170 --> 00:08:09,719
what's stolen will never truly be mine.

157
00:08:10,080 --> 00:08:12,159
During the time I was with Zhou Zeyang,

158
00:08:12,159 --> 00:08:13,940
there was always more trouble
than happiness.

159
00:08:13,950 --> 00:08:15,212
I do like him,

160
00:08:15,520 --> 00:08:16,760
but if breaking up

161
00:08:16,760 --> 00:08:18,760
brings peace back to our lives,

162
00:08:19,479 --> 00:08:21,175
I'm willing to force myself
to start over.

163
00:08:21,560 --> 00:08:22,599
I get it.

164
00:08:23,350 --> 00:08:24,425
A sob story.

165
00:08:25,080 --> 00:08:27,080
You want to return to Jinxin.

166
00:08:27,080 --> 00:08:28,880
Too bad none of us believe you.

167
00:08:28,880 --> 00:08:29,960
Yan.

168
00:08:31,359 --> 00:08:32,719
Jiamin, I believe you.

169
00:08:32,720 --> 00:08:35,190
I've also been through a time
when I forced myself to make a decision.

170
00:08:35,200 --> 00:08:35,879
I understand,

171
00:08:35,879 --> 00:08:36,990
and I'm willing to trust you.

172
00:08:37,000 --> 00:08:38,599
As long as
you've figured it out yourself,

173
00:08:38,599 --> 00:08:39,990
that's more important than anything.

174
00:08:40,280 --> 00:08:42,359
Besides, we're family.

175
00:08:42,359 --> 00:08:43,787
Everyone will welcome you back.

176
00:08:45,200 --> 00:08:45,960
Don't include me.

177
00:08:46,359 --> 00:08:47,200
I don't welcome her.

178
00:08:51,987 --> 00:08:52,800
Qin,

179
00:08:53,062 --> 00:08:54,542
will you let Jiamin come back?

180
00:08:58,200 --> 00:09:00,320
I don't care whether
you truly mean it or not,

181
00:09:00,599 --> 00:09:01,920
I just want to ask you one thing.

182
00:09:02,359 --> 00:09:04,575
Can you take responsibility
for what you're saying?

183
00:09:04,719 --> 00:09:05,359
I can.

184
00:09:06,087 --> 00:09:06,599
Mo.

185
00:09:06,999 --> 00:09:08,080
Shanshan.

186
00:09:08,359 --> 00:09:08,920
I know

187
00:09:08,920 --> 00:09:11,040
I did a lot of things
that upset you before.

188
00:09:11,519 --> 00:09:13,359
I don't expect your forgiveness
right away.

189
00:09:13,759 --> 00:09:16,137
But from now on,
I'll prove my words with actions.

190
00:09:18,160 --> 00:09:20,400
Please give me one more chance.

191
00:09:25,400 --> 00:09:26,320
Qin.

192
00:09:28,680 --> 00:09:29,960
Qin Jiamin, listen.

193
00:09:30,759 --> 00:09:32,719
Everyone in this home is your family.

194
00:09:33,200 --> 00:09:34,920
I hope you won't let everyone down,

195
00:09:36,400 --> 00:09:37,800
especially Shanshan's trust in you.

196
00:09:38,359 --> 00:09:39,800
I won't.

197
00:09:41,200 --> 00:09:41,839
Let's eat.

198
00:09:42,040 --> 00:09:42,359
Mm.

199
00:09:42,800 --> 00:09:43,800
Let's eat, Mo.

200
00:09:48,519 --> 00:09:49,280
Here, Mo.

201
00:09:49,362 --> 00:09:51,212
(Jinxin Food Co., Ltd.)

202
00:09:51,560 --> 00:09:53,200
Ms. Zhuang. Shanshan.

203
00:09:53,200 --> 00:09:55,639
This is a revised product plan

204
00:09:55,639 --> 00:09:57,680
based on last month's sales.

205
00:09:57,725 --> 00:09:59,759
Could you take a look
when you have time?

206
00:10:01,630 --> 00:10:03,437
If there are any issues,
we can discuss them.

207
00:10:03,500 --> 00:10:04,700
I welcome all suggestions.

208
00:10:08,200 --> 00:10:09,080
Qin Jiamin.

209
00:10:10,960 --> 00:10:13,040
You're quite the actress, aren't you?

210
00:10:14,150 --> 00:10:15,837
We all know what you're up to,

211
00:10:16,200 --> 00:10:17,400
so save the performance.

212
00:10:17,960 --> 00:10:18,800
Yan.

213
00:10:19,200 --> 00:10:20,440
It's alright, Shanshan.

214
00:10:20,440 --> 00:10:21,999
I just got back.

215
00:10:21,999 --> 00:10:23,890
I still need time to get familiar
with things again.

216
00:10:28,999 --> 00:10:30,999
Yan, why are you doing this?

217
00:10:32,037 --> 00:10:33,677
Why do you trust her so easily?

218
00:10:34,070 --> 00:10:35,996
Have you forgotten
what she did to you before?

219
00:10:36,087 --> 00:10:37,646
That's all in the past.

220
00:10:37,912 --> 00:10:39,512
Jiamin knows she was wrong now.

221
00:10:39,512 --> 00:10:41,272
We should give her another chance.

222
00:10:41,650 --> 00:10:43,810
Do you really think
she's sincerely changing?

223
00:10:44,512 --> 00:10:45,713
It's only been a few days.

224
00:10:45,720 --> 00:10:47,100
She suddenly turned over a new leaf?

225
00:10:47,112 --> 00:10:48,512
I think she's just acting.

226
00:10:49,100 --> 00:10:50,899
She's not as bad as you think.

227
00:10:53,400 --> 00:10:54,119
Shanshan,

228
00:10:54,400 --> 00:10:55,920
don't be so naïve.

229
00:10:55,920 --> 00:10:57,920
You should learn from your mistakes.

230
00:10:57,999 --> 00:10:59,519
If you keep trusting people so blindly,

231
00:10:59,519 --> 00:11:00,980
aren't you just waiting
to be schemed again?

232
00:11:01,999 --> 00:11:05,119
Yan, don't you get tired of
always being so guarded?

233
00:11:07,119 --> 00:11:08,599
Jiamin already knows she was wrong.

234
00:11:08,599 --> 00:11:09,800
We're family.

235
00:11:09,800 --> 00:11:10,519
Just forgive her.

236
00:11:10,519 --> 00:11:11,200
My, my.

237
00:11:11,200 --> 00:11:13,590
It's exactly because you're this simple
that I'm so exhausted.

238
00:11:14,125 --> 00:11:14,885
Yan,

239
00:11:15,262 --> 00:11:16,743
I know you mean well for me.

240
00:11:17,220 --> 00:11:19,119
But please don't always treat me
like a child.

241
00:11:20,560 --> 00:11:21,999
You're tired, and so am I.

242
00:11:52,225 --> 00:11:54,245
I was going to give you
the application form.

243
00:11:54,912 --> 00:11:55,713
Were you?

244
00:11:56,600 --> 00:11:59,380
Were you about to say you just didn't
get the chance to give it to me?

245
00:12:00,200 --> 00:12:02,320
Were you also going to say
it was all for my own good?

246
00:12:02,320 --> 00:12:03,719
But I really was doing it for you.

247
00:12:03,719 --> 00:12:05,719
Exposing Zhou Zeyang was for my sake.

248
00:12:05,719 --> 00:12:07,400
Being wary of Qin
was for my sake.

249
00:12:07,400 --> 00:12:08,999
Targeting Jiamin was for my sake.

250
00:12:08,999 --> 00:12:09,800
And now

251
00:12:10,200 --> 00:12:12,320
hiding the application form
was also for my sake.

252
00:12:13,359 --> 00:12:15,560
Why do you think I need that from you?

253
00:12:16,359 --> 00:12:17,160
Shanshan,

254
00:12:18,519 --> 00:12:20,800
I came here to protect you.

255
00:12:20,920 --> 00:12:22,359
I hid the application form

256
00:12:22,360 --> 00:12:24,600
because I want you to stay at Jinxin
with peace of mind.

257
00:12:24,700 --> 00:12:25,800
Only by taking charge of Jinxin

258
00:12:25,800 --> 00:12:27,800
can you hold your own fate
in your hands.

259
00:12:28,479 --> 00:12:29,519
I see now.

260
00:12:30,680 --> 00:12:33,599
From the very beginning,
you calculated every step.

261
00:12:34,359 --> 00:12:35,960
Even I became part of your scheme

262
00:12:35,960 --> 00:12:37,680
without realizing it.

263
00:12:39,050 --> 00:12:41,040
Maybe you really think
you're doing this for me,

264
00:12:41,599 --> 00:12:44,560
but I don't need it.

265
00:12:44,560 --> 00:12:47,400
I don't need you scheming
or hurting people for my sake.

266
00:12:47,400 --> 00:12:49,160
It was Qin who saved Jinxin.

267
00:12:49,160 --> 00:12:50,519
It should belong to him.

268
00:12:50,599 --> 00:12:52,680
I don't want to start doubting
my own family

269
00:12:52,800 --> 00:12:55,040
or live under
your one-sided expectations.

270
00:12:55,960 --> 00:12:56,800
So

271
00:12:57,119 --> 00:12:59,987
please stop interfering in my life.

272
00:13:00,000 --> 00:13:00,440
Okay?

273
00:13:31,037 --> 00:13:34,675
♪The old dial tone circles in my ear♪

274
00:13:34,800 --> 00:13:38,112
♪Faded tickets point to a cicada summer♪

275
00:13:38,275 --> 00:13:41,862
♪The videotape
whispers your image in the frame♪

276
00:13:42,162 --> 00:13:45,450
♪Against the light, the plaid shirt
reveals a clear and transparent smile♪

277
00:13:45,675 --> 00:13:49,300
♪I'm a clumsy guest in a frozen scene♪

278
00:13:49,462 --> 00:13:52,800
♪How do I answer familiar lines?♪

279
00:13:52,875 --> 00:13:56,587
♪I know
the train will leave this station♪

280
00:13:56,637 --> 00:14:00,500
♪I know the ending's in a faded future♪

281
00:14:00,562 --> 00:14:06,612
♪Yet I want to approach that warmth♪

282
00:14:07,787 --> 00:14:14,525
♪Even one second rewrites missed lines♪

283
00:14:14,812 --> 00:14:19,087
♪Rewind to 1995,
back to the street we met♪

284
00:14:19,087 --> 00:14:22,387
♪Wind blows through the sycamore leaves
and lands on your shoulder♪

285
00:14:22,462 --> 00:14:26,762
♪I wish I could pause and stop time♪

286
00:14:26,825 --> 00:14:30,475
♪Let unspoken love
be preserved forever as amber♪

287
00:14:30,475 --> 00:14:34,037
♪Rewind to 1995,
gentle touch of fingertips♪

288
00:14:34,087 --> 00:14:37,350
♪Star sparks in your eyes burn my chest♪

289
00:14:37,350 --> 00:14:41,100
♪This looping script
is beyond my saving♪

290
00:14:41,100 --> 00:14:47,812
♪I can only stay with you till the end
in this inverted hourglass♪
